iversity<br />\r\n-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Experiences:</p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin-left: 40px;\\">&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; From October 1991 to May 1998&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Worked in Finance and Accounting Department &ndash; Nam Dinh Power Branch, Power Company Number 1 (PC1)<br />\r\n&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; From June 1998 to April 2004&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Worked in Internal Auditing Department - Vietnam Electricity (EVN)<br />\r\n&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; From April 2004 to August 2008&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Worked in Equitization and Securities Department &ndash; Vietnam Electricity (EVN)<br />\r\n&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; From September 2008 to June 2016&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Member of Board of Supervisors - EVN Finance JSC<br />\r\n&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; From July 2016 - now&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Head of Board of Supervisors - EVN Finance JSC<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<strong><span style=\\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\\">MR. NGUYá»„N XU&Acirc;N ÄIá»†P<br />\r\n</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><img width=\\"120\\" height=\\"150\\" src=\\"/data/upload/image/20150714/mr%20Diep_web.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" /><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Member<br />\r\n-&nbsp;&nbsp; Bachelor of Science (Economics Major) - National Economics University.<br />\r\n-&nbsp;&nbsp; Experiences:</p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin-left: 40px;\\">&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; From August 2007 to November 2007: Forex trading official-&nbsp; An Binh Commercial Joint Stock Bank.<br />\r\n&bull;&nbsp; From November 2008 to June 2011: Invesment Official, Risk Management Official, Internal Audit Official- Lien Viet Commercial Joint Stock Bank.<br />\r\n&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; From June 2011 to present: Bond Trading Group Leader- An Binh Commercial Joint Stock Bank.<br />\r\n&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; From April 24, 2015 to present: Member of Board of Supervisors- EVN Finance JSC.</p>\r\n<p><span style=\\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\\"><strong>Mrs Äá»– THá»Š H&Agrave; &nbsp;</strong></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img width=\\"100\\" height=\\"129\\" alt=\\"\\" src=\\"/data/upload/image/Do%20Thi%20Ha.JPG\\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp; Member<br />\r\n-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Bachelor of Accounting - University of Finance and Accounting; Master of Economics - National Economics University<br />\r\n-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Experiences:</p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin-left: 40px;\\">&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; From 1991 to 2007: Worked at Power Construction JSC No.1; Vietnam Industrial Construction Corporation. <br />\r\n&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; From 2007 to 2016: Worked at EVN Finance JSC - Deputy Director of Accounting Department, Deputy Director in charge of Legislation &amp; Internal Control Department, Director of Internal Audit Department, Director of Accounting Department - Chief Accountant, Assistant Chairman of Board of Management.<br />\r\n&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; From 23rd April, 2016: Member of Board of Supervisors - EVN Finance JSC.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\\"><span style=\\"font-size: medium;\\"><strong>BOARD OF DIRECTOR</strong></span></span><span style=\\"font-size: medium;\\"><span style=\\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\\"><strong><br />\r\n</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p><strong style=\\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\\">MR. B&Ugrave;I XU&Acirc;N&nbsp;DÅ¨NG&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;General Director</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;<br />\r\n<strong><span style=\\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\\">MR. HO&Agrave;NG Máº NH Háº¢I</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><img width=\\"130\\" height=\\"179\\" src=\\"/data/upload/image/Hoang%20Manh%20Hai-6.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" /><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Deputy General Director<br />\r\n-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Bachelor of Business (Banking) &ndash; Banking Academy; Bachelor of Law &ndash; Hanoi University of Law; MBA - Northcentral University (USA)<br />\r\n-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Experiences:</p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin-left: 40px;\\">&bull;&nbsp; From 1995 to 2008: Worked in banking and finance sector, held many important positions in domestic and international audit organizations and financial institutions<br />\r\n&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp; From 2009 to present: Deputy General Director - EVN Finance JSC</p>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<span style=\\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\\"><strong>MR. L&Yacute; Máº NH H&Agrave;</strong></span><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&nbsp;<img width=\\"130\\" height=\\"162\\" src=\\"/data/upload/image/20150115/lymanhha_web(1).jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" /></p>\r\n<p>Deputy General Director</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; -&nbsp; Bachelor of Science ( Major in External Economics) -&nbsp; University of Social Sciences and Humanities- Vietnam National University, Hanoi; Civil and Industrial Engineer-&nbsp; Hanoi Architecture University; Master of Business Administration &ndash; La Trobe University, Australia<br />\r\n-&nbsp; Experiences:</p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin-left: 40px;\\">&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp; From 2001 to 2008: Worked at Agribank, specialized in credit sector and project management. In charge of Branch Deputy Head of Appraisal Department, Deputy Head of Credit Department-cum- Deputy Director of Headoffice building project management department in Hanoi Brach; Head of Admistration Department in Tam Trinh Branch<br />\r\n&bull;&nbsp; From 2009 to present: working at EVN Finance JSC, in charge of Director of Credit Department since July 2012, Deputy General Director since Jan 15th, 2015.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\\"><strong>MR. NGUYá»„N HO&Agrave;NG Háº¢I</strong></span><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img width=\\"130\\" height=\\"162\\" src=\\"/data/upload/image/20150115/nguyenhoanghai_web.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" /></p>\r\n<p>Deputy General Director</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br />\r\n-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Bachelor of Science (Major in External Economics) &ndash; Hanoi Foreign Trade University; Bachelor of Science (Major in Marketing Economic) &ndash; Saxion University, Netherland; Master of Business Administration-&nbsp; Radboud University, Netherland. <br />\r\n-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Experiences:</p>\r\n<p style=\\"margin-left: 40px;\\">&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp; From June 2007 to October 2011: Worked at An Binh Commercial Joint Stock Bank, in charge of Investment Council Member, Head of Investment Department at Head office, Deputy Director of Strategic Client Development Department.<br />\r\n&bull;&nbsp; From February 2010 to May 2014: Worked at ABBANK ASSET MANAGEMENT, in charge of ABB Investment Council Member-cum- Deputy General Director.<br />\r\n&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp; From June 2014 to present: Working at EVN Finance JSC, in charge of Board of Management Assistant, Deputy General Director since January 15th, 2015. <br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong style=\\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\\">MR. L&Ecirc; ANH TUáº¤N</strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><img width=\\"130\\" height=\\"198\\" alt=\\"\\" src=\\"/data/upload/image/20151013/leanhtuan1.JPG\\" /></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div>Deputy General Director</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>- Master of Economics - National Economics University</div>\r\n<div>- Experiences:</div>\r\n<div style=\\"margin-left: 40px;\\">&bull; &nbsp;&nbsp;From 2003 to 2008: Worked at Son La Hydropower Project Management Board - Vietnam Electricity</div>\r\n<div style=\\"margin-left: 40px;\\">&bull; &nbsp;From 2008 to present: Working at EVN Finance JSC - Deputy Director of Fund Arrangement and Credit Department, Director of Trusted Management and Onlending Department; Deputy General Director since September 15th, 2015.</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'admin', 1292643608, 'ducnt', 1467771374, 'english', 1, 2);
