(60, 'news-amp-events', 'evnfinance-news', 'evnfinance-and-song-da-207-joint-stock-company-signing-the-comprehensive-cooperation-agreement', 'EVNFINANCE and Song Da 207 Joint Stock Company signing the Comprehensive Cooperation Agreement', 'admin', '1293520410', 'admin', '1293525331', 'english', 0, 2, '<p>On 25th November 2009, in Ha Noi, EVNFinance Joint Stock Company (EVNFinance) and Song Da 207 Joint Stock Company (Song Da 207) signed the Comprehensive Cooperation Agreement. According to the agreement, the two parties committed to cooperate in investment, investment intermediary, credit and financial consultancy, ect.</p>', '<p>On 25th November 2009, in Ha Noi, EVNFinance Joint Stock Company (EVNFinance) and Song Da 207 Joint Stock Company (Song Da 207) signed the Comprehensive Cooperation Agreement. According to the agreement, the two parties committed to cooperate in investment, investment intermediary, credit and financial consultancy, ect.<br />\r\nSong Da 207, a subsidiary of Song Da Corporation, mainly operates in construction, real estate trading, construction and financial investment services. After 8 years of operation, Song Da 207 has asserted their own brand on Vietnamese construction market with the successful implementation of many large projects, becoming professional contractor in construction field in Vietnam.<br />\r\nAccording to the agreement, EVNFinance committed to grant credit, provide capital arrangement consultancy services; effective management of deposits; corporate finance consultancy services in cash flow management, capital structure optimization, corporate finance restructure; corporate bond and project bond issuing consultancy and guarantee services for Song Da 207.<br />\r\nThe Comprehensive Cooperation Agreement between EVNFinance and Song Da 207 has showed the willingness to cooperate and establish long-term relationship in the principle of voluntariness, equality, mutual benefits and understanding.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', '', '(TCÄL, 26/11/2009)', 1, ''),
(61, 'news-amp-events', 'evnfinance-news', 'evnfinance-to-co-sponsor-establishing-and-investing-in-3g-network-project-of-evn-telecom', 'EVNFinance to co-sponsor â€œEstablishing and Investing in 3G Networkâ€ project of EVN Telecom', 'admin', '1293520515', 'admin', '1293525326', 'english', 0, 1, '<p>On 25th November 2009, the Signing Ceremony of Credit Contract to co-sponsor the project &ldquo;Establishing and Investing in 3G network&rdquo; of EVNTelecom was held in Hanoi with the participation of Vietnam Joint Stock Commercial Bank for Industry and Trade (Vietinbank), Great Asia Commercial Joint Stock Bank (Dai A Bank), Asia Commercial Bank (ACB), EVNFinance Joint Stock Company (EVNFinance) and PetroVietnam Finance Corporation (PVFC).</p>', '<p>On 25th November 2009, the Signing Ceremony of Credit Contract to co-sponsor the project &ldquo;Establishing and Investing in 3G network&rdquo; of EVNTelecom was held in Hanoi with the participation of Vietnam Joint Stock Commercial Bank for Industry and Trade (Vietinbank), Great Asia Commercial Joint Stock Bank (Dai A Bank), Asia Commercial Bank (ACB), EVNFinance Joint Stock Company (EVNFinance) and PetroVietnam Finance Corporation (PVFC).<br />\r\nEVNTelecom, a subsidiary of EVN, has formally received the 3G license in September, 2009. Based on that, EVN Telecom will establish information network infrastructure with nearly 2.500 BTS stations covering 46 percentage of the population after 9 months since licensing date. &ldquo;Establishing and Investing in 3G network&rdquo; is a potential project which will open up many opportunities to EVNTelecom in developing new services, improving competitiveness to expand market share.<br />\r\nEVNFinance together with EVNTelecom and other partners (banks and financial institutes), basing on appraisal results, have agreed to co-sponsor with the total sponsorship of 1.900 million VND for the project. This credit commitment in the context of financial difficulty and present pressure on Vietnam money market can be considered as important initial step to establish and develop credit relationship, capital management, investment, financial consultancy, information exchange and business relationship between EVN Telecom and domestic financial institutes. <br />\r\nAs a focal point to generate, arrange capital and improve effectiveness of using capital for the Electricity of Vietnam and its subsidiaries, after 01 year of operation, EVNFinance has gradually asserted its position by greatly support the capital arrangement for electricity projects, ensuring timely progress of electricity projects.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', '', '(TCÄL 26/11/2009)', 1, ''),
