(47, 'products-amp-services', 'credit-services', 'project-finance', 'Project Finance', 'admin', '1293510288', 'admin', '1293510288', 'english', 0, 2, '', '<p><strong><span style="color: #0000ff">EVNFinance </span></strong>provides a loan to a specific project (carried out by an organisation or a group of organisations).</p>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<strong><span style="color: #008080">Conditions:</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><br />\r\n&bull;&nbsp;Suitable to EVNFinance&rsquo;s strict regulations<br />\r\n&bull;&nbsp;Feasible project (basing on EVNFinance&rsquo;s opinion)</p>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<strong><span style="color: #008080">Benefits for customers:<br />\r\n</span></strong>&bull;&nbsp;EVNFinanceprovides a loan basing on the feasibility and cash flows of the project.<br />\r\n&bull;&nbsp;EVNFinance commits to provide the required amount of capital basing on cash flow of the project.<br />\r\n&bull;&nbsp;Provide worthy services relating to the project in order to assist project&rsquo;s investors.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', '', 'unhide'),
(48, 'products-amp-services', 'credit-services', 'financing-working-capital-for-enterprise', 'Financing working capital for Enterprise', 'admin', '1293510403', 'admin', '1293510403', 'english', 0, 2, '', '<p>In order to support customers in seizing business opportunities, EVNFinance provides prompt and adequate working capital for the traditional customers at competitive interest rate.</p>\r\n<p><br />\r\nIn case of frequent need for working capital for the whole production cycle, EVNFinance will offer short-term loan line, by which customers can draw capital at any time within 12 months. This will help customers to stabilize their financial source and more in control of their in business and production planning.</p>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<strong><span style="color: #0000ff">Types of loan:</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><br />\r\nSeparate lending: Customers can borrow separate loans based on their capital demand for each specific business plan.<br />\r\nLimited lending: Each customer is offered a credit line maintaining in certain period or in business and production cycle according to his business plan.</p>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<strong><span style="color: #0000ff">Terms of loan:</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><br />\r\nEVNFinance offers flexible loan term of up to 12 months and suitable with customer&rsquo;s business cycle.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', '', 'unhide'),
(44, 'products-amp-services', 'credit-services', 'guarantee', 'Guarantee', 'admin', '1293509865', 'admin', '1293509898', 'english', 0, 2, '', '<p>With our strong financial capacity and prestige, EVNFinance will provide customers with effective financial instruments, such as guarantee services.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Customers are offered guarantee services without paying out requirement. They can also reclaim money quickly or extend due date for payment of goods and services, etc. Therefore, even though they are not directly provided funds, customers have financial advantages as if they were actually provided funds. <strong><span style="color: #0000ff">EVNFinance</span></strong>&rsquo;s guarantee services help facilitate smooth conclusion of trade, service, construction, investment contracts and domestic and international transactions.</p>\r\n<p><br />\r\n&bull;&nbsp;Competitive and diversified fee schedules for all types of guarantee<br />\r\n&bull;&nbsp;Terms of guarantee are in accordance with customer&rsquo;s requirements and guarantee application dossiers<br />\r\n&bull;&nbsp;Prompt and convenient procedures<br />\r\n&bull;&nbsp;Given EVNFinance&rsquo;s prestige and capacity, the guarantee service will enhance customers&rsquo; trust before their partners<br />\r\n&bull;&nbsp;Our skilled and experienced team will provide free-of-charge consultancy on the best guarantee services<br />\r\n&bull;&nbsp;Types of security for guarantee are various and flexible (cash-cover, mortgage, collateral..), depending on customer&rsquo;s capacity and prestige<br />\r\n&bull;&nbsp;There are a wide range of guarantees, including guarantee for domestic and foreign loans, bid bond, performance bond, guarantee for payment and stand-by credit, guarantee for product quality, guarantee for advance payment, and others.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', '', ''),
(45, 'products-amp-services', 'credit-services', 'trust-lending', 'Trust Lending', 'admin', '1293509999', 'admin', '1293509999', 'english', 0, 2, '', '<p><strong><span style="color: #0000ff">Senario 1: </span></strong></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="color: #0000ff"><br />\r\n</span></strong>EVNFinance is entrusted a loan by an entrustee through an Entrustment Agreement in order to use Entrustee&rsquo;s money to lend a customer (Financial Institutions or an Enterprise) or a project.</p>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<strong><span style="color: #0000ff">Senario 2: </span></strong></p>\r\n<p><br />\r\nEVNFinance entrusts an amount of money to a Financial Institution or a Bank. The Financial Institution or the Bank will lend that money to a customer.</p>\r\n<p><br />\r\n<strong><span style="color: #008080">Benefits for an Entrustee:<br />\r\n</span></strong>&bull;&nbsp;Attractive entrustment rates<br />\r\n&bull;&nbsp;Good chance to involve in EVN&rsquo;s projects<br />\r\n&bull;&nbsp;Reducing costs and other resources in valuation and assessment.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', '', 'unhide'),
(46, 'products-amp-services', 'credit-services', 'documentory-discounting', 'Documentory Discounting', 'admin', '1293510071', 'admin', '1293510071', 'english', 0, 2, '', '<p><strong><span style="color: #0000ff">EVNFinance</span></strong> offers documentary discounting service to meet the customer&rsquo;s demand for working capital. We will offer the most competitive discounting rate and discounting interest rate.</p>', '', 'unhide'),
