(73, 'products-amp-services', 'financial-and-cdm-advisory-services', 'trust-for-negotiating-and-signing-loan-contract', 'Trust for negotiating and signing loan contract ', 'admin', '1295425501', 'admin', '1295425501', 'english', 0, 2, '<p>Project owners may entrust <strong><span style="color: rgb(0,0,255)">EVNFinance</span></strong> in negotiating and signing loan contracts with domestic and foreign donors.</p>', '<p>Project owners may entrust <strong><span style="color: rgb(0,0,255)">EVNFinance</span></strong> in negotiating and signing loan contracts with domestic and foreign donors.</p>\r\n<p><br />\r\nCustomers with huge and special demand for capital, or foreign loan contracts of special credit and conditions, <strong><span style="color: rgb(0,0,255)">EVNFinance</span></strong> can be entrusted by project owners to:</p>\r\n<p><br />\r\n&bull;&nbsp;Negotiate and sign the loan contracts <br />\r\n&bull;&nbsp;Support the loan disbursement<br />\r\n&bull;&nbsp;Manage the loan</p>', '', 'unhide'),
(74, 'products-amp-services', 'financial-and-cdm-advisory-services', 'cdm-advisory-service', 'CDM Advisory Service ', 'admin', '1295425536', 'admin', '1296037446', 'english', 0, 2, '<p>CDM - Clean Development Mechanism is the mechanism that allows industrialized countries to use financing services (capital sponsor, new technology assistance, etc.) for emission reduction projects (called Carbon projects) in the developing countries, in contrast developed countries will receive credit of emission, known as CER - &quot;Certified Emission Reduction&quot;.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', '<p>CDM - Clean Development Mechanism is the mechanism that allows industrialized countries to use financing services (capital sponsor, new technology assistance, etc.) for emission reduction projects (called Carbon projects) in the developing countries, in contrast developed countries will receive credit of emission, known as CER - &quot;Certified Emission Reduction&quot;.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n<strong><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">Clients: </span></strong><br />\r\n&bull; The electricity enterprises, power project investors interested in CDM.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n<span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);"><strong>EVNFINANCE provides following services:</strong></span><br />\r\n&bull; Advisory service of survey and assessment the capability to develop CDM activities in new invested projects on the field of power and energy saving. <br />\r\n&bull; Advisory service to select independent Designed Operational Entities (DOE) for the projects: representative of investors work with DOE over the process of evaluating and adjusting the project documents on the basis of the comments of DOE.<br />\r\n&bull; Advisory service to implement necessary procedures to register CDM at Vietnamese Designated National Authorities (Vietnam DNA) and the International Executive Board on CDM (International EB).<br />\r\n&bull; Advisory service to choose partners buying Certified Emission Reductions (CERs).<br />\r\n&bull; Supporting to negotiate the contents of Emission Purchasing Reductions Agreement (ERPA).<br />\r\n&bull; Being trusted for trading Certified Emission Reductions (CERs) on the secondary market.<br />\r\n&bull; Acting as trustee or authorized representative (Process Agent) to perform all of the CDM registration procedures, negotiate contracts of purchasing Emission Purchasing Reductions Agreement (ERPA), CERs transactions.<br />\r\n&bull; Being trusted to manage the capital flow of certified emission reductions CERs transactions.<br />\r\n&bull; Being trusted for managing the domestic and international capital sponsored for CDM development activities.<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n<strong><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">Clients&rsquo; benefits:</span></strong><br />\r\n&bull; The project will be implemented with advanced technology, fuel efficiency and high productivity. When the project is recognized and certified CERs by CDM Executive Board of the United Nations (EB), project owners can trade these CERs on the international market in accordance with the Clean Development Mechanism.<br />\r\n&bull; EVNFINANCE is assigned by Electricity Vietnam (EVN) to develop CDM projects of EVN and its subsidiaries.<br />\r\n&bull; EVNFINANCE is acting as a consultant during the development process of CDM projects and takes part in funding and fund arrangements for the project (if necessary).<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>', '', ''),
